      • add

        public boolean add​(long k0,
                   long k1,
                   long k2,
                   long k3)
        Adds key to hash set preserving key uniqueness. 256 bit long encoded in 4 64-bit values
        Parameters:
        k0 - 0-63 bit
        k1 - 64-127 bit
        k2 - 128-191 bit
        k3 - 192-256 bit
        Returns:
        false if key is already in the set and true otherwise.
